data.description: Live at Bordeaux with acclaimed District 6 Schools! 3 Bed/2 Bath one-level living on a fenced in over-sized lot! Tenderly loved and immaculate home is ready for a new owner - Master Bedroom on the Main Floor, Screened-In Porch, Granite Countertops, Rope Lighting, Decorative Chair Rail and Luxe arched hallways! Minutes from several of the best District 6 Schools, Shopping, Restaurants along with easy access to the highways! Enjoy the convenience of a community pool and clubhouse! Relax in the little things like a tankless water heater that keeps that hot water hot without running out. Stainless Steel appliances surround your kitchen island and beautiful granite countertops . So much to offer and with inventory this low very little time to see it! Be sure to put this one on your short list of homes to see now!
